                            <li><strong>Promissory Note:</strong> An unsecured legal IOU for the equity payout. Must include an IRS-compliant interest rate. <button id="info-link" class="text-blue-500 underline">(Why is interest required?)</button> <a class="report-link" href="#" data-report-anchor="#s4-1" target="_blank">(details)</a></li>
